      h1.p-2.mx-5 Say Hello
      form(method='POST' action='/contactus')
          p
          | Have questions? Need Help? 
          br
          | Your Feedback Makes a Difference! Tell us what you think
          br
          .form-floating.mx-5.py-2
            input#fullname.form-control(type='text' placeholder='Please enter your full name' name='fullname' 
